dBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T04:53:50.000Z","msg":"濕地私怨"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:02:03.000Z","msg":"扭屎忽花 扮傷唔落場 爆sms出黎扮無辜<br />\n其實老早同佢講唔再用佢<br />\n比你你仲用唔用佢？用下腦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214908e0c42b6bb07731d6d93ba7870a644c73fb","tid":660262,"uid":143768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:07:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今季車問題<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 走左costa 夏神同willian要做多好多野</span><br />\n2. 走左matic 跟住bakayoko頂唔到佢個位<br />\n<br />\n其實買barkley係應該想用佢踢352個攻中<br />\n但係bakayoko踢到屎咁 唔出得<br />\n唯有踢343 咁就無佢位<br />\n同埋條友黎左無耐訓練已經話又傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今季車夏天真係要買一個中場 未必係防中<br />\n可能中場中 而且係要世界級既<br />\n前鋒就唔洗買啦 我覺得其實mola達有可能踢得好既<br />\n佢始終初來英超既時候好似7場入6球定5球<br />\n係信心問題姐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加上排352，冇埋Willian ，mark死世三就好難攻"},{"pid":"2d14002f986257a30a6c5118d4ed0ab3b81644b0","tid":660262,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T06:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}